# Article V — Constitutional Principles

## Section 5.1 — Purpose

The Constitutional Principles establish the permanent architectural laws of the byDebut ecosystem.

Unlike implementation decisions, which may evolve as technology advances, these principles define the invariant characteristics of every Living Story Universe.

Every engineering decision, business decision, governance policy, Artificial Intelligence workflow, and future platform capability shall comply with these principles.

No implementation may violate them.

